41
00:02:08,760 --> 00:02:09,600
Go to hell!

42
00:02:19,440 --> 00:02:20,720
Gather all officers
in the station now.

43
00:02:20,720 --> 00:02:22,360
Find Ye Ying
and Song Pa's location.

44
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:22,840
Legal or illegal,

45
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:23,840
