Huo Xiao's father never knew
what was good for him

114
00:05:12,080 --> 00:05:13,440
and got in the way of
my money.

115
00:05:13,440 --> 00:05:15,320
Ye Hong refused the merger

116
00:05:15,320 --> 00:05:17,360
and even
threatened me with

117
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:19,800
Longxing Group's
gang crime business.

118
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:21,920
