back from me.

121
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:29,560
But in the end?

122
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:31,040
All those who opposed me

123
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:32,760
ended up with

124
00:05:32,760 --> 00:05:34,240
