Ye Ying.

173
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:03,720
Huo Xiao?

174
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:04,920
Why are you here?

175
00:08:07,840 --> 00:08:09,440
- Are you okay?
- Are you alright?

176
00:08:11,280 --> 00:08:12,680
What do we do now?

177
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:14,360
All the evidence is gone.

178
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:18,120
Only Song Pa's confession

179
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:19,920
can bring him to justice.

180
00:08:21,400 --> 00:08:22,600
I've already

181
