make it out alive.

191
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:18,920
Scared?

192
00:09:21,160 --> 00:09:22,120
No.

193
00:09:24,800 --> 00:09:26,320
I'll never lose you again.

194
00:09:53,120 --> 00:09:54,440
Out of bullets, huh?

195
00:09:56,280 --> 00:09:57,600
At death's door

196
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:59,040
