231
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:27,040
Now that Father has passed away,

232
00:11:27,040 --> 00:11:28,520
we went through so much.

233
00:11:28,520 --> 00:11:29,560
I never thought

234
00:11:29,560 --> 00:11:31,520
we'd meet again.

235
00:11:31,520 --> 00:11:33,160
And even stay by each other's side.

236
00:11:33,680 --> 00:11:35,400
That's already healed
so many regrets.

237
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:37,240
Sis.

238
00:11:37,240 --> 00:11:39,560
It's time for me to
find my own path.

239
00:11:46,960 --> 00:11:48,040
Dad.

240
00:11:48,040 --> 00:11:50,320
Song Pa has finally faced justice.

241
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:51,280
Now,

242
00:11:51,280 --> 00:11:52,760
