243
00:12:02,280 --> 00:12:03,200
Boss.

244
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:06,520
Thanks to all your trust.

245
00:12:07,760 --> 00:12:09,520
I officially take over
as the new Leader.

246
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:11,280
From this day on,

247
00:12:11,280 --> 00:12:13,920
